news.title: NHMA: Statewide Zoning Mandates Didn’t Help NH’s Housing Crisis
news.summary: Statewide zoning mandates enacted in 2025 did little to address housing affordability and risked undermining the local decision-making that is central to New Hampshire’s identity, according to a whitepaper by the New Hampshire Municipal Association.

news.title: Teamsters President Sean O’Brien kicks off reelection campaign
